00:46:34.670 --> 00:46:41.660
So it's more about educating,
I think, the client and also

00:46:41.660 --> 00:46:44.670
having the agency to
be a little bit more,

00:46:44.670 --> 00:46:46.730
I guess, courageous
with the approach.

00:46:46.730 --> 00:46:49.380
Because there's always
this time where they say,

00:46:49.380 --> 00:46:51.090
