what is cool, and what is not.

00:46:58.100 --> 00:46:58.970
Right?

00:46:58.970 --> 00:47:00.260
That's not theirs.

00:47:00.260 --> 00:47:01.940
That's why you are there.

00:47:01.940 --> 00:47:04.430
And once that happens,
once the client

00:47:04.430 --> 00:47:08.420
becomes confident and accepts
what the agency have to do,

00:47:08.420 --> 00:47:10.340
then I think the
content in the region,

00:47:10.340 --> 00:47:12.502
because we have the
capabilities to produce,

00:47:12.502 --> 00:47:14.210
is that they're going
to be a lot better.

